<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #222;">
  <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
  <p>A request was made to reset the password for {{email}}.</p>
  <p>Use the link below to choose a new password:</p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{callbackUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 16px; background: #c62828; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>If you did not request this change, you can ignore this email.</p>
</div>
